from seed.client import SeedApi

client = SeedApi(
    token="YOUR_TOKEN",
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)
client.imdb.create_movie(
    title="string",
    rating=1.1,
)
snippet.async_client:
from seed.client import AsyncSeedApi

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    token="YOUR_TOKEN",
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)
await client.imdb.create_movie(
    title="string",
    rating=1.1,
)
